title: [Royal Court, Anodheles Way]
description: Moonlight shines through the swaying, sparse canopy and glimmers softly as it dances across darkened puddles.  Faint echoes of scratching and scurrying seem to originate from a decrepit wishing well embraced by the spindly limbs of a weeping willow.

Shadows play across the muddy puddles that darkly reflect the swaying, sparse canopy overhead.  Faint echoes of scratching and scurrying seem to originate from a decrepit wishing well, embraced by the spindly limbs of a weeping willow.
